main event: Two or three objects were observed visually and through binoculars, appearing, brightening, dimming, and disappearing very low on the horizon in the WSW for 1 to 2 minutes.
interesting points: The objects were seen one at a time, seemingly one at a time.
The reporting officer concurs that the sighting was probably caused by naval aircraft practicing night landing exercises on aircraft carriers in the area.
There were two or three objects observed.
